import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import MessageForm from '../components/MessageForm'
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar'


const Chat = () => {
    return(
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col md> 
                    <Sidebar />
                </Col>
                <Col md>
                    <MessageForm />
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Chat
